{
  "texts": [
    "Students were informed that the only purpose of the test was to help the course instructor recognize their knowledge levels, allowing for adjustments to the instruction and course content to cater to the overall class proficiency.",
    "Importantly, students were assured that their test would not impact their grades in any way.",
    "Afterwards, on the 4th, 7th, and 12th weeks of the semesters (i.e., the weeks of practice sessions), interventions were conducted.",
    "After each session both qualitative and quantitative data were collected.",
    "The qualitative data included the ChatGPT interaction logs."
  ]
}